<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٣٨ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ , أَنَّ أَبَا بَكْرٍ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْحِيتَانُ كُلُّهَا ذَكِيٌّ حَيَّةً وَمَيْتَةً»</span> ,<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٣٩ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> <span class="c2">«وَمَا طَفَا عَلَى الْمَاءِ فَلَيْسَ بِهِ بَأْسٌ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>